# Project Standards

- Use hexagonal Architecture.
- Keep clear separation between domain, application, and infrastructure.
- Use TypeScript strictly.
- Use Prisma as ORM.
- Prefer dependency injection.
- Avoid business logic in controllers.
- Follow TypeScript / JavaScript naming conventions (see `naming-conventions-typescript.mdc`).
- Follow detailed architecture rules in `.cursor/rules/architecture/`.
